  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/81015823/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u81015823-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="祭祀" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/81015823/">祭祀</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          1小时前          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:尼采 思想</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46125143/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46125143-5.jpg" class="pil" alt="非洲酋长" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46125143/">非洲酋长</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          今天晚上          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">读尼采读懵逼了，早点看这本就好了。对尼采思想的介绍很好。看到后面，近代哲学各个流派或多或少都和尼采有关，而且尼采对潜意识认识已经如此深了，弗洛伊德到像是拾人牙慧一般😳</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
